  "keyFeatures": [
    "Phoenix LiveView web UI with real-time streaming chat and decision graph visualization",
    "Interactive CLI with REPL-style interface and markdown rendering",
    "Persistent decision graph with 7 node types tracking reasoning across sessions",
    "Repository intelligence with ETS-backed indexing and relevance ranking",
    "Token-aware context window with automatic budget allocation",
    "11 built-in tools for file operations, search, shell, git, and decision tracking",
    "Multi-provider LLM support via req_llm (16+ providers, 665+ models)",
    "Session persistence with SQLite storage",
    "Permission system with per-tool, per-path approval",
    "Sub-agent search for parallel codebase exploration",
    "MCP protocol server and client support",
    "LSP diagnostics integration",
    "Architect mode with two-model workflow (planning + execution)"
  ],
